title: Hobitit (The Hobbits) 1993 Finnish mini-series with English subt
description:
This is a 1993 9 episode mini-series from Finland. Even though it is called The Hobbits only the first episode adapts parts of that novel. The other eight are an adaptation of the Lord of the Rings. This is all nine episodes with optional English subtitles.

"The Hobbits"
Episodes: 9
Original Airdates: March 29-May 24, 1993
Runtime: 3 hours, 28 minutes, 2 seconds (~23 minutes each)
Aspect Ratio: 4:3
Video Format: MP4
Spoken Language: Finnish
Subtitles: English (SRT files)
Source: Unknown. Seems to be a VHS rip or something like that, although the quality looks better than most VHS tapes and I don't see any logos for it to be a TV rip.
Filesize: 605 MB (~67 MB per episode)

Director: Timo Torikka
Writer: Timo Torikka
Starring: Matti Pellonpaa, Martti Suosalo, Vesa Vierikko, Ville Virtanen, and others
